The '''Platform-7''' was a giant [[Droid/Legends|droid]] in the city [[Sath]] of the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Samaria/Legends|Samaria]]. It controlled several datascreens and [[Computer/Legends|computers]] all at the same time. It was a variant of the [[BRT supercomputer/Legends|BRT supercomputer]].

